  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一下这个FastAPI医疗系统的整体架构。核心是有六个业务模块：患者管理、医疗服务提供方、服务项目、预约、理赔，还有支付。另外我想加一个审计模块，这个比较特殊，要用Bedrock AI来做智能分析。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Patient Module",
        "Provider Module",
        "Service Module",
        "Appointment Module",
        "Claim Module",
        "Payment Module",
        "Audit Module with Bedrock AI",
        "FastAPI Application"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，这七个模块都放在FastAPI Application这个大框里对吧？我想确认一下关系：患者、提供方、服务这三个模块是数据源，它们跟预约和理赔都有关联？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Patient Module",
        "Provider Module",
        "Service Module",
        "Appointment Module",
        "Claim Module"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，P、PR、S这三个是核心实体，它们都要支持预约和理赔两个流程。然后理赔模块会触发支付，同时理赔和支付都需要被审计追踪。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Patient Module",
        "Provider Module",
        "Service Module",
        "Appointment Module",
        "Claim Module",
        "Payment Module",
        "Audit Module with Bedrock AI"
