    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画出七个模块的节点，把P、PR、S放在左边一列，A和C放中间，PM和AU放右边。连线关系我按你说的来画。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Patient Module",
        "Provider Module",
        "Service Module",
        "Appointment Module",
